Croogo Image2  plugin for Croogo 1.4 above!!
------------------------------
Modification of original Image helper boundled with Croogo.
Automatically resize or crop (also cache) image and returns formatted IMG tag

For use this plugin with previous versions of Croogo, switch branch to 0.1

Usage
------------------------------
$this->Image2->resize($path, $width, $height, $method = 'resizeRatio', $htmlAttributes = array(), $return = false, $server_path = false);

Params:
* @param string $path Path to the image file, relative to the webroot/img/ directory.
* @param integer $width Image of returned image
* @param integer $height Height of returned image
* @param string $method resize method (resize, resizeRatio, resizeCrop, crop)
* @param array    $htmlAttributes Array of HTML attributes.
* @param boolean $return Wheter this method should return a value or output it. This overrides AUTO_OUTPUT.
* @param string $server_path Local absolut path to file

